metadata.description:
Tranhumanist artist Joshanne Dar, explores themes of post-feminist and post structural identities through her phenomenological dialogue with the digital.

These portraits are part of The Electric Drama investigation for her 2020 Covid-19 lockdown collection and form the unique mini series of four, virtual 3d portrait models of the artist. Each hidden 3d model has a different set of perforations, characterised through Joshanne's interactions with the machine.

This first release contains the original secret 3d model of the artist, which can be redeemed only by the token owner*

https://www.instagram.com/joshannedar/
